{"title":"","options":[{"title":"Write to us","kind":"url","type":"persist","events":[],"content":"https://www.nsandi.com/contact-us#write-to-us"}],"content":"<p>If you want to close an old Savings Certificate, <strong>please write to us at NS&amp;I, Sunderland SR43 2SB</strong>, providing any relevant account details.</p>

<p>You can find more information of what to include in your letter by clicking the link below.&nbsp;</p>
